			--specify no class for <class> below, use NONE (which matches
			--only if the compiler does not report the error in a particular
			--class).  <result> can be:

			--	syntax_error  { <class> <line-number> ";" ... }+
			--		
			--		Matches if compiler reported a syntax error on each
